RULE 1- NO CHEATING DURING TOURNEY'S
RULE 2- REGULAR MESSAGE WILL BE SEND OF INFORMATIVE THING'S
RULE 3- THERE WILL BE ONLY 2 LEADER. NO ONE ELSE WILL BE MADE LEADER
RULE 4- IF A PERSON HAVE A BOT ID SO HE/SHE HAVE TO COME WITH THEIR REAL ID IN TOURNAMENT'S
RULE 5- IF A PLAYER OF OUR TEAM MAY ACCUSED CHEATED BY LICHESS LIKE THIS PLAYER ARTIFICIALLY INCREASES AND DECREASE HIS/HER RATING THEN HE/SHE WILL BE KICKED

NOTE ABOUT TEAM ETIQUETTE- lichess.org/page/team-etiquette
